{"word":"G3842 - πάντοτε - pántote - pan'-tot-eh - Alway","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πάντοτε</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>pántote"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pan'-tot-eh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Alway"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"எப்போதும், எப்பொழுதும், எக்காலத்திலும் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"at all times, always, ever"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3956 - πᾶς - pâs - pas/3956\">G3956</a> and <a href=\"#/G3753 - ὅτε - hóte - hot'-eh/3753\">G3753</a>; <i>every when</i>, that is, <i>at all</i> times: - always (-s), ever (-more)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}